                <answer>
                    <p>A gets <m>56 + 10 + 8 + 4 + 1 = 79</m> points</p>
                    <p>B gets <m>42 + 30 + 16 + 16 + 2 = 106</m> points</p>
                    <p>C gets <m>28 + 40 + 24 + 8 + 4 = 104</m> points</p>
                    <p>D gets <m>14 + 20 + 32 + 12 + 3 = 81</m> points</p>
                    <p>So the winner is Boris (B).</p>
